  "Description": {
    "English": "An ancient object, unearthed from the depths of a planetary cave system. Its surface is cold to the touch, and is curiously polished despite its age.<br><br>A fusion of metal and rock, these cubes have proved resistant to industrial processing. As such, they are of value only to collectors.<br><br>Can be sold at a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Galactic Trade Terminal</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "从行星洞穴系统深处出土的古代物件。表面入手冰凉，尽管年代久远，但却光滑得出奇。<br><br>这些立方体是金属和岩石的融合体，难以进行工业加工。因此，它们只对收藏家有价值。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">银河交易终端</span>出售。",
    "TencentChinese": "密度大的金属物品，很久之前形成于星系各处的地下网络。<br><br>极其稀有，价值很高。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "從星球洞穴系統深處出土的古老物體。其表面觸感冰涼，雖然年代久遠，卻異常光滑。<br><br>此類箱體為金屬與岩石融合而成，經證實難以進行工業處理，因此僅有收藏價值。<br><br>可在<span class=\"name name-technology\">銀河交易終端站</span>出售。"
  },
